## Requirements
1. Add a specialized handler for "Mistral Instruct v0.3" format
2. Format: user turns wrapped with `[INST]`/`[/INST]`, system messages prepended to first user turn, `</s>` after assistant turns
3. Register with template auto-detection in `common_chat_try_specialized_template()` - distinguish from existing Ministral 3 handler by checking for the ABSENCE of `[SYSTEM_PROMPT]`
