**Location**: `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775499895165-dbprgz/common/chat.cpp`, line 1688 (just before `return std::nullopt;` at line 1690)

