- Does NOT contain `[SYSTEM_PROMPT]` -- distinguishes from Mistral v7 and Ministral 3 (which the Ministral 3 handler already checks for, but this provides a clean negative guard)
- Does NOT contain `[AVAILABLE_TOOLS]` -- distinguishes from Mistral v3, v3-tekken, and Nemo templates which have native tool calling
- Does NOT contain `<<SYS>>` -- distinguishes from Llama 2 variants

